The paper deals with compression of deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of a novel quantization scheme, which is a technique commonly used in information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper proposes a compression algorithm that takes into account the impact of quantization on the accuracy of the network, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
